data.description: Discover this exquisite home in Schertz, Texas, just a stone's throw from Randolph AFB, offering an exceptional living experience or a lucrative rental income opportunity. With 4 bedrooms and 3 baths, this beautifully maintained residence boasts a spacious layout complemented by lofty ceilings that enhance its airy ambiance. The heart of the home features a large modern kitchen, complete with an island and bar seating, perfect for hosting and everyday meals. An inviting loft area upstairs adds to the living space, while the bedrooms offer generous room for relaxation and privacy. Step outside to find a backyard primed for transformation into your personal oasis, featuring a quaint covered patio for outdoor enjoyment. Situated in an excellent location, this home presents the ideal blend of comfort and convenience, making it a must-see for those seeking their next abode or investment in Schertz. Two bedrooms downstairs with full bath.   Two Water Heaters, Two AC Units, Water Softener, Sprinkler System, Jack and Jill Bath Upstairs, Tie Flooring Down, Gas Cooking, Grand Entry, Schertz Cibolo Universal City School District, Desirable Location.
